java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Map<java.lang.Object,java.lang.Object>
public class VARStatus
extends java.util.Properties

The status of a repserver module/process. The basic list of status indicators include uptime, totalMemory, freeMemory, class path and system properties. Additional indicators may be added using the put() method since this class extends java.util.Properties.
